#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:379
msgid "Night falls... The scouts reported at midday that those accursed soldiers of Uria were headed towards our town. It’s going to be a very long night waiting for them to arrive."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_2
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:384
msgid "Assuming they don’t somehow make it here sooner than that. Sigh... It wasn’t enough for them to burn and ransack Tyannes. Damn it, why don’t the elders send us reinforcements?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:389
msgid "Meh. Ever since this war started they have cared little about safety — not just ours. It’s rumored that the country itself would fare very poorly against another foreign invasion."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_2
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:393
msgid "Well, I’ve heard that the elves have..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_3
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:397
msgid "On guard! Three strangers approach from the southern road!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:423
msgid "Halt there! Identify yourselves, strangers!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:427
msgid "We are travelers. We don’t plan to stay in your town for more than one night. You don’t need to know who we are."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_2
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:431
msgid "Sorry, but we were ordered not to let anybody... pass... She’s... beautiful."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_3
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:436
msgid "A faerie? Wh— what’s one of your kind doing so far from the northern lands?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:440
msgid "As I said, we don’t plan to stay for more than one night. Just let us in."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:455
msgid "Who is that? Hey, the cloaked one!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:459
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:251
msgid "Eh?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:463
msgid "Aaah!! Necromancer!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_3
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:467
msgid "Quick! Alert the—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:471
msgid "You are not alerting the entire town of his presence, are you? Such a handsome man could spend the night doing... more worthwhile things than fighting us..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_3
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:475
msgid "Erm... I..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:479
msgid "I don’t know what the hell your purpose here is, but we do have important things to do this night, such as defending the town from your cursed henchmen!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:483
msgid "Henchmen? Do you see anyone else accompanying us? No? Well, then."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:490
msgid "Eh! That you don’t <i>seem</i> to bring anyone with you does not mean you cannot somehow summon them later! We heard rumors of the infernal warriors coming to our valley!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:495
msgid "Infernal, you say?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:507
msgid "Clad in black armor, bearing flags with impaled skulls at the top, and said to smell especially funny?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:512
msgid "Those are our enemies as well. We have had many encounters with them before. Perhaps we could be of help, <i>if</i> you would be so kind as to let us into the town."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:517
msgid "Let them come in at once! We are in need of all the help we can get if we want to live another day."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:522
msgid "Yes, sir! As you command, sir!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:542
msgid "Strangers, please help us. I am sure the gate guards already told you of the situation..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:547
msgid "Yes, they did."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:552
msgid "Well, well. I have heard of necromancers helping the northern country’s cause, so I... suppose you can be trusted. Although, if you turn out to be working for our enemies we would be doomed either way. I beg of you to aid us in this battle; all we have left nowadays is the town militia, for which we can barely afford proper weapons."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:557
msgid "We’ll help you. Just don’t ask names."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:562
msgid "That’s... a very dubious request..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:570
msgid "There is someone else coming with us. I hope you will not mind his presence here as well."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:575
msgid "Well, I..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:616
msgid "Ugh, a goblin? Riding a wolf? You cannot be serious! Your kind is not welcome around these parts after the poultry farmers’ guild incident."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:621
msgid "No, no, no! I mean no harm! Just passing by with my friends, that’s all! Willow is also a very well behaved lady, you aren’t even gonna notice her presence."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=guard_6
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:634
msgid "Sir! We’re receiving reports of enemy forces approaching from the northern hills!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:639
msgid "Blast it — we did not anticipate them arriving so soon! Everyone, to arms!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:655
msgid "We failed to protect the town..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:669
msgid "Curse you, heretics! The Iron Council shall punish you for your deeds!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:681
msgid "I do not think so."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:690
msgid "We will be eternally thankful for your help, travelers! If there is anything we can do in return..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:695
msgid "No problem; we just need provisions and directions for our journey to the northern country."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:700
msgid "Traveling north, eh? There is a mountain pass to the northeast — it used to be a very accessible trading route before the war began. Nowadays it is plagued by dark cultists and their undead minions, and the Grand Council has done nothing to clean it up."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:705
msgid "Thanks for the information, we may as well take that path then."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:710
msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:715
msgid "We <i>control</i> the dead. We need not worry about them."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:739
msgid "Sometimes, your loved ones must be willing to sacrifice their lives for a greater cause."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:753
msgid "Their reinforcements are here! There is no way we can keep the town from devastation at this point!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/storytxt.cfg:70
msgid "High Pass"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=Mal Ciphan, type=Lich
#. [side]: id=Nyadien, type=Draug
#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:44
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:164
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Search_for_the_Past.cfg:87
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:134
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:176
msgid "team_name^Undead"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=Mal Ciphan, type=Lich
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:87
msgid "Mal Ciphan"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=Nyadien, type=Draug
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:207
msgid "Nyadien"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#. [event]: type=Orcish Archer, type=Orcish Archer, type=Skeleton, type=Orcish Grunt, type=Revenant, type=Revenant, type=Deathblade, type=Dark Adept, type=Skeleton Archer, type=Orcish Grunt, type=Revenant
#. [scenario]
#. [event]: type=Shaxthal War Drone, type=Shaxthal Enforcer Drone, type=Shaxthal Demolisher Drone, type=Chaos Cataphract, id=Celwyngyr, type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Morol, type=Lich, id=Mal Fyrgwynn, type=Demon Warrior, gender=male, id=Demon Lord Alavys
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:289
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:157
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:247
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/09_The_Triad_part_1.cfg:887
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:208
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:271
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:232
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:561
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1166
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/02_01_Return_to_Raelthyn.cfg:663
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:531
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:545
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/04_01_Outpost_of_Hell.cfg:660
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/04_01_Outpost_of_Hell.cfg:677
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/05_Pass_of_Sorrows.cfg:636
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1628
msgid "Defeat all enemy leaders"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:306
msgid "This place gives me chills. Perhaps this path was not a good choice after all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:312
msgid "Pah. Leave your worries behind, there is nothing to..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: type=Necrophage
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:345
msgid "Groaaar!!!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:350
msgid "... and who called upon you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:355
msgid "So it is as the townsfolk warned us — this pass is infested with undead. We’ll have to give them a final rest before we can proceed any further."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:360
msgid "Aww, this will be boring."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Ciphan
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:376
msgid "Ahhh, the traitors! Never again will you see the sunlight, for I shall feed your impious souls to Yechnagoth!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:381
msgid "The same old tune. These goons should seek a new job or something."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nyadien
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:390
msgid "You, Galas! You abandoned us in the valley! You left us all to die!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:395
msgid "Nyadien? But..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:400
msgid "Do you know him?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:405
msgid "He was the leader of the patrol group that replaced mine just before the Chaos Empire invaded our valley."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:410
msgid "Elf, know that Galas did not have the power to stop that invasion, but the Chaos Empire no longer has a leader. There is nothing that should force you to roam this world anymore!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nyadien
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:415
msgid "I will personally make sure you don’t go unpunished, traitor!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:420
msgid "It is a waste of time to try to deal with this pile of bones. The necromancer who raised him probably used some malign spell to infect his soul with hatred towards every elf who outlived him."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:547
msgid "It’s beginning to snow... Galas, we probably should avoid spending too long in this pass — it seems like it could easily become a deathtrap, especially with the undead controlling it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:552
msgid "I agree, the snow could not only hinder us significantly but also turn us into easy prey."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:562
msgid "We are taking too long! We need to hurry up if we don’t want to be buried alive in this place!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:580
msgid "I am vanquished, but I curse your race to never see a day of peace or joy again for the rest of eternity!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:592
msgid "So many times... I forget how many times they have said that."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:606
msgid "Honestly, with your fearsome steed you should be more than able to reach your destination without us, Igor."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:611
msgid "You’re kidding, right? There’s no way we’d be able to get past all the smelly skeletons alone! I don’t wanna become one of them zombies while I’m still young!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:616
msgid "<i>(snicker)</i> I could arrange for you to become a more dignified skeleton warrior if you prefer..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:621
msgid "Eeek!!! No!!!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:626
msgid "Will you please stop tormenting him, Malin."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:631
msgid "Fiiiiine. <small>Someone needs a sense of humor... <i>mutter mutter</i>...</small>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:636
msgid "The ears aren’t just for show, you know. We <i>can</i> hear you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:645
msgid "It seems like there is a much bigger storm approaching..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:654
msgid "This doesn’t seem good at all — the storm has finally reached this pass and we’ll be buried under the snow. We should not have tarried here for so long!"
msgstr ""

