msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Grulock
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:75
msgid "Grulock"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Chaos Razerman, id=Zygred
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:121
msgid "Zygred"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#. [else]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:207
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:348
msgid "Move Elynia to the top edge of the map"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:237
msgid "She hasn’t wanted to talk to us for days. Is our destination...?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:242
msgid "Yes, I gather that her plan is still to strike at Wesmere before the Northlanders have an opportunity to launch a proper offensive or even hear of our situation. Damn, for all I know our messengers and their ship could have been destroyed by the enemy already."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:247
msgid "I heard that the Grand Council has been hesitant about pressing on this war ever since your victory in the Empire’s so-called capital. They think they’ve won already."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:270
msgid "Is everyone ready for battle?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:276
msgid "Er, battle?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:281
msgid "Our scouts didn’t go unnoticed, and they found a couple of well-armed enemy outposts ahead. This will most certainly not be a safe journey across the dry remains of Wesmere."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:309
msgid "Has it even occurred to you that our little struggle in their headquarters on that accursed peninsula has put their forces in motion again to protect what little remains of Yechnagoth?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:316
msgid "Of course it has. But there’s no time to discuss this now. Let’s move out."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:327
msgid "These disgusting demons are vanquished at last!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:332
msgid "Yes, but we must proceed quickly and cautiously to the northeast nevertheless. More troops will come if we give them the opportunity to regroup."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:376
msgid "Onwards we go, now!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:400
msgid "We cannot advance without securing our path first!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:414
msgid "It’s still my opinion that we are running a large risk with your current plan."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:419
msgid "Was it any better to not take risks at all in that fortress, though?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:428
msgid "I don’t know what you are trying to imply, but I may as well remind you that I wasn’t the only one to hesitate and that <i>he</i> would not have survived the attempt without his lower half like I did. It was <i>your</i> assigned task to practice that spell beforehand and <i>you</i> failed to do so — don’t involve me in <i>your</i> mistakes."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:433
msgid "<i>(glaring at Mal Keshar)</i> ..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:439
msgid "Pagh, let’s get on with this, everybody! We haven’t got much time!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/storytxt.cfg:338
msgid "Ambush at the Gates"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Chaos Cataphract, id=Mendryr
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:100
msgid "Mendryr"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Haldaran
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:128
msgid "Haldaran"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Hell Guardian, id=Elgamal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:144
msgid "team_name^Wesmere Defense"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Hell Guardian, id=Elgamal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:154
msgid "Elgamal"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:282
msgid "Due to the Wesmere curse, the time of day is always chaotic during this scenario"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:291
msgid "There’s an alarming amount of movement in the southern hills. It would seem an entire battalion has been following our steps since we left Kalari Peninsula."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mendryr
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:305
msgid "The Council was right in their assessment of the situation. The elf witch and the lich have amassed an army of orcs and undead mercenaries to raid Fort Ænthal. It seems we arrived in the nick of time. To arms!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Haldaran
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:310
msgid "To arms! For the Dark Lady!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:323
msgid "I sort of expected that. It might prove tricky to advance with those buffoons on our heels. On the other hand, the fortress ahead doesn’t seem to be very well guarded."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:328
msgid "Very well, then. Let’s take them down."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:333
msgid "I do feel something is amiss, though. We should be cautious... especially since our leader appears to be giving us commands without thinking things through."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:338
msgid "If you think <i>you</i> could do a better job at leading the orcs..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:343
msgid "It’s not my intention to have <i>anything</i> to do with them at all. I just want to make sure you keep your feet on the ground — well, whenever that is an appropriate thing to do, anyway."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:351
msgid "What did you say about the fortress not being well guarded, lich?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:356
msgid "I stand corrected. We <i>may</i> need a better strategy."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:368
msgid "We have failed... H— how? *Ugh*"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:380
msgid "Forgive us, Lady..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:392
msgid "You are about to find out that Yechnagoth is no more, fool."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:408
msgid "I depart from this world to embrace the power of Uria..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:413
msgid "Not likely, but you will certainly embrace the cold touch of death on the other side, heh, heh."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elgamal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:418
msgid "You... You haven’t seen the full extent of her power... You haven’t seen the great things she’s done for us... You understand nothing... Nothing... at all..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:430
msgid "Now that you’re dead, all that has suddenly become irrelevant, hasn’t it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:462
msgid "It’s over now, fiends. Flee while you can, and make sure the Triad hears of your shameful defeat at our hands."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:468
msgid "It’s over now. There’s nobody left to obstruct our path but those artificial abominations."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:475
msgid "<i>(snicker)</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:480
msgid "So, Wesmere is just ahead. What are you going to do now, lass?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:485
msgid "I want to discuss some plans with the three of you right now, in fact. Come with me."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/storytxt.cfg:338
msgid "Departure"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:60
msgid "You seem even more upset than usual, Elynia. What would the matter be this time?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:69
msgid "I don’t think I could bear more losses after what happened to Galas. My plan was not to <i>fight</i> in enemy lands, but rather to <i>infiltrate</i>. This battle was not part of the plan — we were to part ways right before reaching this fort."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:74
msgid "Wait... You planned to enter the hive on your own, without us? That’s just... stupid! You don’t know for sure what lurks beneath besides the Shaxthal creatures we have encountered so far! What if that woman or Mal Hekuba are awaiting there?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:79
msgid "I was hoping you could provide me with a few of your best undead warriors, in fact."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:84
msgid "Lady, that’s suicidal! From what we’ve heard, <i>nobody</i> could survive a confrontation with those horrors without support! Allow us to protect you until you reach the entrance to the caves at the very least!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:89
msgid "I refuse to send any undead down there unless you allow me to go with you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:110
msgid "What’s your motivation, Malin? What makes you want to accompany me now that neither Galas nor Anlindë exist in this world?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:119
msgid "I have been tempted to ask you the same question for a while, actually. I know you cared about the boy much like you cared about Argan, and I have sensed your grief following his death. And yet, somehow you have been in denial about it — perhaps <i>afraid</i> to admit that losing him had a greater effect on your self than losing Argan. I suppose it could just be a matter of time, seeing as how Argan disappeared from your life much longer ago."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:124
msgid "But even though you want to pretend none of this is the truth, your demeanor makes it all evident to us. Now you seem to seek vengeance against Uria’s followers, especially Elyssa. What’s the point of wasting the gift of eternal life to pursue such an ephemeral goal, I ask?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:133
msgid "You have not answered... my question..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:138
msgid "Probably because I don’t need to. I don’t have a motive to do anything anymore. My foolish mission to erase the orcish species from Irdya failed too long ago!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:143
msgid "Is it redemption that you seek?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:148
msgid "I don’t know! That’s what you asked when I first met you, remember?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:159
msgid "We aren’t accomplishing anything. My lady, please reconsider—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:164
msgid "We’ll secure the hive entrance together, but from that point onwards it will be only Mal Keshar and I, and whoever wants to go with us except for you two."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:170
msgid "Wh— Why would that be, my lady?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:175
msgid "We are going to need some capable soldiers alive to alert the Grand Council if neither we nor our messengers make it back. I want you to immediately head back to the Far North should we not return to the surface within one day."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:180
msgid "Very well, then. I am... unsure about what strategy — if any at all — you have in mind to defeat or destroy whatever you are going to face in that place, but... Your quest is noble. I wish you the best of luck to complete it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:185
msgid "If I ever return to our island, I’ll make sure our people hear of your bravery and your many sacrifices. I am sure you’ll succeed in this last mission, my lady."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:196
msgid "Thank you... It really means a lot to me."
msgstr ""

