#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:476
msgid "Death of Durvan"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:188
msgid "Frankly, when the village chief said ‘capable’ I was expecting something better."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:193
msgid "It’d be a grave mistake to underestimate us, lass. Life ’round here ain’t easy these days, and we have to be prepared to deal with anything."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:198
msgid "I’m well aware of that, having lived in the wilderness myself before, but these are mostly novices and untrained youths!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:203
msgid "The chief wouldn’t want to send off veterans on the chance that our home is attacked again. Anyway, we’d better get going. Look out for the trolls that control this road — they hunt unwary travelers and eat them alive."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:214
msgid "Blast! I wasn’t counting on this happening!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Reck
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:235
msgid "Reck don’t like humans on his base. We smash them!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Reck
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:247
msgid "Reck dying... and don’t know why."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:262
msgid "That big troll was hoarding quite a decent sum of gold in these ruins."
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: id=Dremorran, type=Fugitive
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:293
msgid "Dremorran"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:353
msgid "Cic"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:354
msgid "Glynvan"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:355
msgid "Quorren"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:356
msgid "Caror"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:357
msgid "Danon"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:380
msgid "I hear some commotion ahead..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Quorren
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:395
msgid "Drop everything you’re carrying with you gal, and we <i>may</i> spare your pretty neck!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:400
msgid "We don’t have time for this—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:405
msgid "We can’t just leave that poor girl at their mercy! We must help her!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:410
msgid "(<i>sigh</i>) Of course, that’s what I was planning to do anyway."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:415
msgid "Save Allyna from the bandits"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:419
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:579
msgid "Death of Allyna"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:432
msgid "Alas! I never got a chance to see the great towers of the capital!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:437
msgid "We shouldn’t have let this happen!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:494
msgid "Oh, thank you for saving my life, sir, I’ll be forever grateful! Is there anything I could do to repay you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:499
msgid "Hm, actually, it is this lass here who is leading us..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:513
msgid "She’s the legendary Lady of Light!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:518
msgid "Oh, I see! I beg your pardon, my lady."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:523
msgid "May I ask what business brings a young girl like you to such a dangerous location alone? What’s your name, anyway?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:528
msgid "I’m Allyna of Dalbloom, from the eastern border. It’s a very tiny village, so you may not have heard of it before. I was sent on a mission to deliver an important message to the Grand Council."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:533
msgid "Hm, I see. We happen to be on a similar mission ourselves. I would strongly suggest that you join us — it’s a miracle that you have made it this far through these uncivilized lands in one piece. What do you think?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:538
msgid "Yes! —I mean, if it doesn’t bother you, of course. Sure it is uncivilized around here — I don’t think I have ever seen a town get ransacked like that before..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:546
msgid "What are you talking about?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:551
msgid "The bridge town ahead was captured by a large armed band. I turned back as soon as I could, but some of their brutes chased me, and then I found you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:556
msgid "Sounds like we may have to cleanse the town a bit before proceeding, then."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:561
msgid "Good plan. Gods, I never thought Talwyn would fall like that..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:575
msgid "Defeat the bandit leader in Talwyn"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Dremorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:595
msgid "No! All our efforts have been in vain!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:617
msgid "Onwards we go, to the capital!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:622
msgid "So are you truly the Lady of Light? I’ve heard many amazing stories about you! Do you mind if I ask you some questions?"
msgstr ""

