#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:475
msgid "Death of Anya"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:267
msgid "There are so many different flowers in this field! It’s beautiful!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:272
msgid "Indeed it is."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:291
msgid "My lady, there are encampments ahead, apparently occupied by elves! This doesn’t look right!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:326
msgid "Certainly not — they shouldn’t be this close to Aragwaithi territory, so I presume they belong to the hostile faction. Everyone prepare for battle, and let’s hope for the best."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:351
msgid "May the Lords of Light protect us..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:361
msgid "They have assembled an army!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:371
msgid "Not just that, but they also have support from the metallic creatures of Uria!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:381
msgid "My lady, what do you suggest we do?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:386
msgid "I wish we could just entirely avoid casualties, but that’s not going to happen."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:395
msgid "I fear for the fate of the elves who sent that call for help to the Council..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Telan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:407
msgid "Who is it that dares defy the power of the Lady of Light?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:412
msgid "You, I presume. I am the only Lady of Light that there is on Irdya, and you have been deceived into fighting against me and the Grand Council of the Northern Peoples in favor of a dark cause, one that betrays the memory of our civilization and our leaders."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Telan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:417
msgid "You are nothing but a blatant impostor working for the human bastards — a dirty, treacherous impostor!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:422
msgid "Take her back to the encampment! I need to ask a few questions..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Telan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:427
msgid "I refuse to answer to the likes of you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unidë
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:449
msgid "The traitors... they have slain me..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:461
msgid "Those elves who willingly choose to support the forces that seek to destroy our world don’t deserve to live."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:466
msgid "(<i>mumbling</i>) That seems rather hypocritical coming from you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:471
msgid "I can hear you, Zynara."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Ethanin-Adrael
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:487
msgid "I shall not fall today!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:501
msgid "He’s escaping!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:625
msgid "How do you do that, girl?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:630
msgid "Do what?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:635
msgid "You seem able to heal your own wounds without any effort. I haven’t heard of other faeries of the deep forest having that power."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:640
msgid "Ah. Well, I have had this ability for as long as I can remember."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:660
msgid "This conflict didn’t begin just now. When Galas and I last visited the northern country, a civil war was already raging due to Inodien’s death. The rumors pointed at the Iron Council’s intrusion in our lands and affairs, but we didn’t have the opportunity to confirm anything."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:665
msgid "Ah, the struggle that resulted in the banishment of the elves from the country. I remember that."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:670
msgid "Much elvish blood has been shed today. I swear that whoever is behind this shall pay with their own life — no matter what it takes."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:756
msgid "Elynia! I’m so glad to see you again after so long..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:761
msgid "Unarye, what happened? We were heading towards the eastern forest to meet with you when we stumbled upon this incursion. How could our enemies advance this far?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:766
msgid "Indeed we owe you a few explanations, and I apologize for arriving late, but our forces have been severely weakened. Come with me, and I’ll explain all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:771
msgid "My lady, do you know this elf?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:776
msgid "She is one of Galas’ friends, Unarye, and she’s been collaborating with the Grand Council ever since we left to infiltrate the Empire. I know she can be trusted. Now, let’s go."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:786
msgid "My lady, I’ve just heard rumors that the elves are already advancing towards Raelthyn."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:791
msgid "That explains why they haven’t crushed us yet despite our poor performance. This was a foolish move. It’s best that we fall back to aid in the defense of the central region, quickly."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:131
msgid "The Plan"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Elvish Lord, id=Lord Ardamién
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:77
msgid "Lord Ardamién"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Elvish Shyde, id=Miryath
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:90
msgid "Miryath"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:133
msgid "Everyone here is restless, and the elvish leader is nowhere to be seen..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:138
msgid "Ah, here she comes!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:157
msgid "I apologize once again for keeping you all waiting."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:162
msgid "It’s no problem, really."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:167
msgid "The reason we moved out of the way to the Aragwaith country is that we originally thought our fallen kin would chase us and leave the humans alone. As we all just saw, of course, we were mistaken. Our own people have managed to retrieve some valuable information from the enemy settlements, though. Listen carefully..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:172
msgid "We are listening, my friend."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:177
msgid "The impostor who calls herself the Lady of Light has amassed a varied army of elves, humans, barbarians and Shaxthal creatures, apparently as part of a plan to reorganize the Chaos forces and strike the human country from the east while keeping their troops busy in the west. Not only have they gotten support from Inodien’s successors, but they have also made contact with elvish and human barbarians from lands farther to the east — peoples whose existence was unknown to us thus far."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:182
msgid "Their base of operations is said to be located in Telchior’s Hold in the Valley of Elynia — the very place whence we fled under Galas’ command following the Chaos invasion. Something deeply wrong must have occurred there after our departure. As I recall, the last time we met you mentioned that Lord Lédinor was possessed by Uria."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:187
msgid "That’s correct, indeed."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Ardamién
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:192
msgid "The information we have could be a fabrication intended to mislead us into thinking the valley has some relevance in the greater scheme of things, but it’s not possible to disregard the danger this foul new alliance poses. If the northern lands fall now, the Chaos Empire will have won the war even without their Emperor or capital."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:197
msgid "We are in the middle of restructuring our forces to protect the eastern front for as long as we can, even if the Grand Council isn’t available to coordinate efforts with us."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:202
msgid "Elynia, you lead many capable warriors and you have the support of the undead. If you could infiltrate the valley in the meantime and vanquish the impostor, we could put an end to the war on this front."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:207
msgid "But... I know nothing of the valley other than that it lies in the middle of the desert — fighting in such an environment could be disastrous!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Miryath
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:212
msgid "The impersonator is a coward and she isn’t going to lead her minions on the front line. If anything can be done about her, it’ll have to be at her base."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:217
msgid "You are a powerful warrior and you have more experience in these matters than any of us present. You helped Galas and Mal Keshar infiltrate the Chaos Empire before. I’m sure you will be successful in this task."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:226
msgid "Very well. We’ll travel to your old home to purge this plague and strike down the false Lady of Light."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:231
msgid "Thank you, Elynia — thank you all. I’m sure that under your command the mission will be a success. Now, I must go to discuss our plans with our field commanders."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:253
msgid "But, my lady, the Ruby! What if it’s a trap?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:258
msgid "We’ll have to deal with the trap if that’s the case. This is more important!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:263
msgid "But Elorran is waiting for us!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:268
msgid "Please inform him of our next mission and convince him to be patient."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:273
msgid "... Very well, then..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: type=Errant Soul
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:160
msgid "The Voyage Home"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Pigork
#. [side]: type=Orcish Slayer, id=Bratar
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:41
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:67
msgid "team_name^Orcs"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Pigork
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:55
msgid "Pigork"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Orcish Slayer, id=Bratar
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:81
msgid "Bratar"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Goblin Rouser, id=Vultraz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:91
msgid "Vultraz"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Goblin Impaler, id=Gargaz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:105
msgid "Gargaz"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:119
msgid "team_name^Desert Creatures"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:176
msgid "team_name^Desert Spirits"
msgstr ""

#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:195
msgid "Mount Boombadil"
msgstr ""

#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:200
msgid "Fort Gralseth"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:277
msgid "Secure the orcish settlement to the southeast by defeating all enemy leaders"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:301
msgid "The desert... I never thought I’d have to see it again."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:306
msgid "Ugh. I feel unwell in these dry and bright lands."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:311
msgid "It can’t be helped. Dark faeries are frail creatures that revel in the shadows of the greatest and densest forests. Really, the desert is no place for you. I am sorry for dragging you along."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:316
msgid "Oh, my lady, it’s not like I’m going to melt away from a little excess sunlight. I just need some time to adapt to this environment, that’s all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:321
msgid "My lady, if you’ll allow me to complain... we can’t just march across the desert without stopping to rest!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:333
msgid "The scouts reported the presence of orcs bearing the Chaos banner in a settlement ahead to the southeast, in the Gralseth region. Stopping to rest here would be very risky with those fools around, but perhaps we could force them out and replenish our supplies."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:338
msgid "Excellent!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:343
msgid "A word of caution, though. Ever since the Fall, the many victims of the disasters which devastated Irdya have been endlessly wandering across lands like this, preying on the souls of the living."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:365
msgid "They are particularly weak by themselves and our arcane fire should be enough to banish them from our world. However, our less experienced fighters should not take their chances fighting them alone."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:379
msgid "Time to get moving."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:414
msgid "I banish you from this world! Go now to your deserved rest!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:420
msgid "Begone, wandering spirit!"
msgstr ""

#. [floating_text]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:447
msgid "banished"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:466
msgid "Oooooh, gryphon eggs! If we take them and let them hatch, do you think we would be able to train gryphon mounts so we can take them to battle? I heard that a famous prince in the Golden Age did that and then won against the evil queen while riding the largest gryphon ever seen!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:471
msgid "I think the desert heat is getting to your head, girl. Perhaps you should refresh yourself at the river for a bit?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:476
msgid "B— but... I swear it’s true!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:495
msgid "Ahhhh... There’s no feeling like putting my feet under refreshing, flowing water... I miss the northern forests..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:500
msgid "Where do you come from, anyway? You couldn’t have spent your whole life traveling with Elorran and Tara."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:511
msgid "Oh... Of course not. It’s just... it’s complicated."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:522
msgid "If you don’t feel like telling me more about yourself right now, I can understand — I’m just curious, that’s all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Bratar
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:530
msgid "Chief! The faerie! The faerie and her pets are approaching from the northwest!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Pigork
#. "Necromancer" should be translated in a gender neutral fashion
#. if possible to keep their identity ambiguous (there are two
#. necromancers in the Iron Council, one is female (Mal Kendria)
#. and the other is male (Mal Hekuba).
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:539
msgid "Ah, just as the necromancer told us. Excellent news. More meat for our wolves!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vultraz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:545
msgid "Yes, more meat for our pigs! Er— I mean wolves!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:595
msgid "A sandstorm! We won’t be able to continue marching like this!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:600
msgid "This small inconvenience shall not stop us! Onwards!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:608
msgid "My lady, are you sure this is a good plan?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:613
msgid "It’s better than tarrying here for too long, so it’s good enough for me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vultraz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:626
msgid "Eaaaagh..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gargaz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:638
msgid "Argh! No!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Bratar
#. "Send our messenger back to the valley, immediately!"
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:651
msgid "They are more than we expected! Send our messenger back to—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:672
msgid "Blast it! Their messenger escaped!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Pigork
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:684
msgid "... useless... insects..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:699
msgid "You retrieve 104 pieces of gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:717
msgid "Maybe this wasn’t such a good idea after all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:722
msgid "I wasn’t counting on that messenger and his swift mount. Regardless, our presence here was both predicted and awaited — this decidedly spells bad news."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:727
msgid "But I told you so!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:732
msgid "I <i>did</i> expect a trap from the very beginning too, girl. We— I have been in situations like this before..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:737
msgid "But this time I won’t let them succeed."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:745
msgid "Valen just informed me that the impostor’s forces are advancing towards Raelthyn. That can only mean Unarye and her troops fell in battle. This is hopeless."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=Elynia
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:180
msgid "Proximus"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#. [side]: type=Chocobone, id=General Lorelath
#. [side]: type=Elvish Hero, id=Cithraldin
#. [side]: type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Gerumanen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:72
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:92
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:131
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:165
msgid "team_name^Northern Defense Line"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Chocobone, id=General Lorelath
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:109
msgid "General Lorelath"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Elvish Hero, id=Cithraldin
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:148
msgid "Cithraldin"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Gerumanen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:182
msgid "Gerumanen"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:242
msgid "According to the map Unarye gave us, the valley entrance is just ahead."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:247
msgid "Good."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:258
msgid "Don’t you think it is unsafe to be here all alone, though?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:263
msgid "There’s nothing suspicious around here, so... No, I don’t think so. We are both capable of defending ourselves against desert animals."
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Lich, id=Mal Zynavu, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:298
msgid "Mal Zynavu"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:319
msgid "Well, let’s see how you fare on your own against <i>me</i>!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:327
msgid "Wh—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:360
msgid "—<b>Who</b> are you in truth? <b>ANSWER!</b>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:365
msgid "It saddens me to admit that my master was a very misguided person — his destruction was only a matter of time. Uria’s power is the greatest force that’s ever graced us. We could avoid wasting so many lives all over the continent if everyone accepted her offer and joined her cause."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:370
msgid "So <b>you</b> were in the country working for the Triad all this time? <b>YOU BETRAYED US!</b>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:375
msgid "I am not the only one! Even those pitiful northerners have grown weary of this pointless war and seek easier alternatives. Now, give me that staff. Oh, and don’t forget you are not in possession of godlike powers anymore — I can and will kill you if you don’t concede."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:418
msgid "<i>They</i> are also willing to help..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:482
msgid "—GAH!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:526
msgid "Anya! Durvan! How did you know? I—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:531
msgid "My lady, we’d never leave you alone in the darkness. After all, it <i>is</i> our element!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:536
msgid "There’s a lot of movement in the hills to the south, my lady. The northern defense line is preparing for battle, and so should we!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:560
msgid "Elynia must destroy Mal Zynavu by herself"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:571
msgid "You may attack Mal Zynavu only with Elynia"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:607
msgid "I didn’t come from so far to the former home of my people to be defeated by a traitor and coward."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#. The truncated word is "Elynia".
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:628
msgid "El— my lady?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:633
msgid "I <i>have</i> done this before, thanks to Argan and Malin. Although I am not as good as them with spirits, unfortunately..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:638
msgid "Your staff... the Ruby’s glowing!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:661
msgid ""
"Elynia can no longer recruit <b>Ghosts</b>.\n"
"\n"
"However, she still has access to any Ghost line units already present in her recall list, and she is now able to recruit <b>Vampire Bats</b>."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gerumanen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:677
msgid "I can see her friends there... he, he..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:682
msgid "Ignore them — strike down the faerie first!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:694
msgid "Who is your leader? Who is awaiting us in the valley and who is my impersonator?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:699
msgid "I work for the Iron Council! I have no idea who—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:704
msgid "You... are... <b>LYING</b>!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:775
msgid "How could you..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:788
msgid "It’s over now."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:797
msgid "My lady..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:806
msgid "Just ‘Elynia’ will do, friends."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:815
msgid "What should we do now?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:820
msgid "There is no turning back, and the impostor must be preparing to confront us or flee from the valley. Whichever is the case, I am going to find her and burn her to ashes. You must contact Elorran immediately to notify him of Zynara’s betrayal. It’s very probable that he is in danger."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:825
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:392
msgid "Very well!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:830
msgid "Everyone else, prepare for what I hope will be our last battle."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:835
msgid "Yes, my lady!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:843
msgid "The main troops are coming..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:214
msgid "And then there was Chaos"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#. [side]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Kaerus-Aganan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:54
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:83
msgid "team_name^Telchior’s Hold"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:73
msgid "Adel"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:75
msgid "Kethael"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:76
msgid "Midnolan"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Kaerus-Aganan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:97
msgid "Kaerus-Aganan"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Gutwrencher Imp, id=Galael
#. [side]: type=Ancient Lich, id=Mal Ryagath
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:109
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:213
msgid "team_name^Base Defenses"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Gutwrencher Imp, id=Galael
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:125
msgid "Galael"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Ancient Lich, id=Mal Ryagath
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:227
msgid "Mal Ryagath"
msgstr ""

#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:280
msgid "Telchior’s Hold"
msgstr ""

#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:285
msgid "Belandras’ Bridge"
msgstr ""

#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:290
msgid "Alenaril’s Pass"
msgstr ""

#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:295
msgid "River Toldrin"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:340
msgid "Elynia must defeat the false Lady of Light by herself"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:341
msgid "Defeat all other enemy leaders"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:343
msgid "The false Lady of Light gets killed by a different unit"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Adel
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:369
msgid "Sirs, the impostor has arrived with her army! The northern defense line is—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kaerus-Aganan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:374
msgid "Ha! Ha! That is no army. I thought the northern elves would be more kind to their so-called savior! Ha!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:379
msgid "Behold, the usurper arrived to challenge us in our own headquarters. What a pitiful effort! To arms! Take her down and bring me her head and the staff she stole from me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kethael
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:384
msgid "Yes, my lady."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Midnolan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:389
msgid "As you command, my lady!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:404
msgid "They seem quite loyal to her despite the state of their home."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:409
msgid "Indeed, something is seriously amiss about these elves. If only we could prove she is the impostor, perhaps they would then listen to reason."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:414
msgid "What do you suggest, my lady... Elynia?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:419
msgid "Stay clear of her and allow me to confront her by myself."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:424
msgid "Very well..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:444
msgid "Dedicated to Elynia-Thanadria of Wesmere, Lady of Light and Protector of the Elves of Irdya."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kaerus-Aganan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:456
msgid "Protect the Lady of Light! Argh—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:471
msgid "I— the Lady of Light... why..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:502
msgid "The impostor escaped!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:507
msgid "This isn’t good. Since we couldn’t unmask her in front of her subjects, they will summon reinforcements and fight us to the death. We must retreat immediately!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:557
msgid "I shall never be defeated by vile impostors like you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:562
msgid "Do you truly believe your own lies? Why don’t you show these elves what you are capable of? Your great powers as the Lady of Light? <i>Who</i> are you, and why are you posing as me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:567
msgid "Your end is at hand. I shall not answer. Guards! Kill her!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:591
msgid "Anariel"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:592
msgid "Eldulas"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:593
msgid "Vinon"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:642
msgid "Back, you fools!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Eldulas
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:722
msgid "What is this? She emanates such a radiant light!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vinon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:732
msgid "... Wha— What are we doing?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:737
msgid "Do not hesitate! Kill her! <b>Now!</b>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vinon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:746
msgid "Who... Who should we trust?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anariel
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:751
msgid "My lady... Elynia! The Lady of Light! I remember you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:760
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08B_Destiny_part_1.cfg:1943
msgid "No..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Eldulas
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:765
msgid "... We have been deceived..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vinon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:833
msgid "What have we done?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:861
msgid "This is <i>not</i> over yet!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: race=elf
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:891
msgid "The false Lady of Light has escaped!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:919
msgid "We still need to defeat the other commanders!"
msgstr ""

#. [else]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:923
msgid "Defeat all remaining enemy leaders"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:941
msgid "Their reinforcements have arrived and they have surrounded the valley! This is hopeless!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:954
msgid "That fiend retreated into the Shaxthal hive."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:959
msgid "Her crimes against the unity of the elvish civilization must not go unpunished. I shall pursue her underground if need be."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anariel
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:964
msgid "My lady, we cannot let you go underground alone! It’s become an exceedingly dangerous place since the new hive was completed."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Eldulas
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:969
msgid "We haven’t seen him or her ourselves yet, but the humans have been spreading rumors of the arrival of a powerful ally of the impostor! They might be awaiting you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:974
msgid "My lady, I— I mean Elynia, let us go with you, please!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vinon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:983
msgid "If there’s anything else we can do to try to amend our grave mistake..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:988
msgid "Let’s go together."
msgstr ""

