#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:547
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/04_01_Outpost_of_Hell.cfg:679
msgid "Death of General Bardyl"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:555
msgid "You’ll continue to control General Bardyl and his troops until the end of the next scenario"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:566
msgid "This is taking too long — I begin to worry for Elynia..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:573
msgid "Nah, there she comes."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:603
msgid "Elynia, you are back! Is that... the journal?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:608
msgid "That’s correct."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:613
msgid "So, is that General Bardyl fellow going to help us assault Aran-Balgur then?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:618
msgid "Indeed he is, but not specifically because of my advice; he was already giving consideration to the idea because of a rumor that’s been running through his troops as of late. It appears someone successfully ‘interrogated’ a captured enemy soldier and got some information about the source of the local raids and the ongoing invasion. What they know suggests that there is indeed a portal in Aran-Balgur."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:623
msgid "I shudder to wonder exactly how this information was obtained. I know from experience that the men in the service of the Empire are either completely ignorant of their superiors’ plans, or instructed to commit suicide before being captured, and the sorcerers and demons are too powerful to contain."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:628
msgid "I guess now we should all advance towards Aran-Balgur?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:633
msgid "Exactly. And we should be careful."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:650
msgid "The road to the south leading to Aran-Balgur is said to be well protected by powerful demons, and there’s also an enemy guard post obstructing our path. Furthermore, we may stumble upon their main invasion army at some point. The only reason Fort Astar still stands is that they don’t perceive Bardyl’s forces as a threat stationed here. However, the moment they see his little army marching towards their territory, they will not be as merciful."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:655
msgid "So it rests on us and our followers, I take it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:660
msgid "Exactly."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:693
msgid "And so, it begins."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:701
msgid "If you don’t mind me asking, sir, are you sure about this?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:706
msgid "Of course I am. The Grand Council has neglected us for long enough, and those damned bastards from hell are getting increasingly bored of playing with us. As much as I find her kind disgusting, if the faerie’s troops and power are as impressive as she promised we’ll recover Aran-Balgur before long. And if there’s a portal in there and we can destroy it, we’ll regain the Council’s blessing as well."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:724
msgid "Time to tear those evil creatures to bits! We will make them pay, oh yes..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:729
msgid "This goblin fellow seems really invested into this, doesn’t he?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:734
msgid "Apparently he was close friends with Lord Galas and Mal Keshar, and also someone else... Elynia hasn’t told me much about that woman in particular, which is saying something considering how difficult it is to get her to talk about the others in the first place."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:739
msgid "Are you sure you should be prying that much, though? It sounds like a very personal subject for her."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:744
msgid "I know, I know... I just wish she would open up and not shoulder so much grief alone when we are all in this together. But perhaps you are right, it’s not my place to intrude."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:806
msgid "Lord Nar-hamoth demands the blood of the northern scum! Charge!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:821
msgid "I remember that name — I believe it’s one of the fiends of the Iron Triad."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:826
msgid "So the rumors Elorran heard are true? That guy is said to be the least competent Demon Lord of all, and yet Uria trusts him over most for some reason."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:831
msgid "We’ll soon see how competent he is on the battlefield, then."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:907
msgid "So you finally decided to challenge me directly? Hopefully this will be an entertaining fight! For the glory of the mother of Urvatha!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:924
msgid "Die, pathetic Irdyan rats! DIE!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1017
msgid "Ha! Not bad, but I was just warming up! Now, let us see if you can handle THIS!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1047
msgid "Oh, come on! That’s just cheating!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1058
msgid "You do not tire of combat easily, eh? I’m impressed! Shall we have a third round then?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1064
msgid "Will you stop doing that, you fiend?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1073
msgid "Ha! Your strength and resourcefulness have not gone unnoticed by the Guardian of Life! I too can respect an enemy that perseveres against impossible odds, Elynia-Thanadria."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1099
msgid "Alas, that stubbornness of yours shall be your and your kind’s undoing!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1114
msgid "Hm. Very impressive, indeed. Despite being such lowly rats, you sure seem to be capable of grand feats when given the right motivation. Ahh, yes, as that hapless bastard Argan found out the hard way. Would that we had not met each other as enemies in a never-ending war, don’t you agree? It is just as unfortunate that my presence is currently required elsewhere..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1119
msgid "Stop him before he escapes!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1124
msgid "I shall eagerly await the day we meet again!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1151
msgid "Come back here, you coward!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1156
msgid "... Fleeing the battlefield seems a conventional tactic for the highest-ranking servants of Uria. Mal Hekuba did so in both of our previous face-to-face encounters as well. I don’t think we ever got a taste of his true might before he decided to fuse his own putrid body with those artifacts."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1161
msgid "That may have been for the best, though."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1166
msgid "Perhaps. Still, I would be grateful if I never had to deal with their limitless arrogance again."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1184
msgid "This operation was a disastrous mistake. Their shock troops are heading here now, and the faerie’s reinforcements are all but useless. Perhaps if we surrender they’ll at least spare our lives."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1214
msgid "Well played, faerie. Not only you deliberately misled us about your numbers, but you also omitted the fact that you consort with necromancers. This changes everything."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1219
msgid "Not necessarily. Today’s events would indicate that together we can build a formidable opposition force. Is this not what you wanted? An opportunity to retake Aran-Balgur, your former home? Is it not what your men desire as well? Or would you prefer to stay here and defend Astar against an enemy with a plan? Tell me, how many soldiers have deserted since the Glamdrol incident?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1224
msgid "I specifically pointed out your deception; I did not say I would retract, and that’s not an option at this point unless I were looking for a mutiny. I’m done speaking to you for now."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1233
msgid "Elynia, are you sure about this? You did admit before that your judgment might not be—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1238
msgid "I’m not really heeding my judgment anymore, girl. It’s just a hunch I have... I have to return to Kalari and find this Demon Lord of the Storms, if it’s the last thing I do."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: type=Chaos Invader,Chaos Raider
