msgid "Current Objective:"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:923
msgid "Talk to the guard captain"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:954
msgid "Who goes there?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:966
msgid "Sir, I have been sent by the Demon Lord of the Storms to bring a message to—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:971
msgid "Is it anything you aren’t allowed to pass on to me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:976
msgid "... Yes, quite so. I would prefer to talk to the Fire in pe—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:981
msgid "The Fire does not want to see anyone right now in her chamber, or anywhere else for that matter. She said so herself: “I don’t want anyone coming into this fortress tonight”. Maybe those deaf sluggards at the main gate need a lesson or two...?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:990
msgid "What’s your name, girl?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:995
msgid "Vyrelyam, sir."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1000
msgid "I hadn’t seen your face around before. But there’s something oddly familiar about it..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1005
msgid "Is that so? ... Perhaps you may also recall torturing an elf or two..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1014
msgid "YOU—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1030
msgid "Well... that didn’t work as planned. We must find a way to open that gate by ourselves."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1033
msgid "Melor"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1034
msgid "Irumia"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1035
msgid "Harakas"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1040
msgid "Move your leader back to the entrance chamber"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Irumia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1068
msgid "There she is!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Melor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1073
msgid "Your illusions can’t deceive me, faerie witch!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Teremor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1106
msgid "Seize her, quickly!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1111
msgid "There goes our infiltration plan. To arms!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1150
msgid "Find a way to open the main access gate"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1188
msgid "Proceed through the main access gate"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1221
msgid "And thus I descend into the darkness of Uria’s key stronghold on Irdya..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1223
msgid "Ergea’s words were clear: we do not have a chance to win this war and purge the corrupted goddess’ influence from this earth; not without the power hidden beneath Kalari."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1225
msgid "I do not intend to stand watching while she turns our ruined world into breeding grounds for her invasion army. Neither could I bear to live knowing that it is in her plans to tear another world apart and threaten our very reality to quench her dreadful thirst for power. I have to do something to prevent that."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1227
msgid "No matter the cost."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1313
msgid "elynia^This is not the right corridor. We must find a way leading to the transport room."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1319
msgid "elynia^That is not the right corridor. We must find a way leading to the transport room."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1343
msgid "Just a bunch of gold coins. Too bad that they are rather weighty and we have no use for them at this time."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1364
msgid "There’s nothing in this chest."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1400
msgid "This potion flask seems important. Let the Lady of Light come to examine it."
msgstr ""

#. [object]: id=potion_of_life
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1458
msgid "Potion of Life"
msgstr ""

#. [object]: id=potion_of_life
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1459
msgid "This potion grants the Regenerates ability, allowing the unit to heal itself 8 HP per turn or remove the poison effect."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1470
msgid "Hm, this might prove useful later."
msgstr ""

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1495
msgid "Potion of Magnificent Taste"
msgstr ""

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1498
msgid "The potion’s stupendous and reinvigorating taste heals the unit by 1 HP."
msgstr ""

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1548
msgid "Legendary Sword"
msgstr ""

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1550
msgid "This sword, forgotten by time, once belonged to a legendary hero who presumably died in a glorious and dignified fashion like real heroes are wont to do. Unfortunately, since then it has rusted beyond use, and as the unit picks it up it snaps in half. The sword is now only marginally better than a small rock in combat — not that Elynia has any units that are trained in sword-fighting anyway."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1597
msgid "Should this unit take it?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1599
msgid "Take it."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1611
msgid "Leave it."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1639
msgid "This small axe is not particularly suitable for combat at close quarters, but it may come in handy as a throwable weapon."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1640
msgid "This small axe could be useful in the hands of a trained man or demon fighter."
msgstr ""

#. [object]: id=throwing_axe
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1645
msgid "Small Axe"
msgstr ""

#. [object]: id=throwing_axe
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1646
msgid "The unit wielding this weapon may use it for long range combat to inflict some considerable blade damage."
msgstr ""

#. [effect]: type=blade
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1656
msgid "throwing axe"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1705
msgid "The poison in the jar could be poured on claws or weapons and used against living opponents in melee combat to increase attack efficiency through its devastating effects on their health."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1706
msgid "This large jar contains poison that could be poured on claws or weapons and used against living opponents by a trained melee fighter or a staff-wielding magic user."
msgstr ""

#. [object]: id=poison_jar
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1711
msgid "Poison Jar"
msgstr ""

#. [object]: id=poison_jar
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1712
msgid "The unit employing this foul-smelling death catalyst can poison living opponents by dealing damage with its melee attacks."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1780
msgid "We must all enter the transport room together — nobody should be left behind."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1786
msgid "Gather all your on-map units in the transport room"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1925
msgid "Now what?"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Lumeril Guard, id=Agathylas
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2006
msgid "Agathylas"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2100
msgid "Mal Boras"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Lich, id=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2107
msgid "Mal Gulgolet"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2179
msgid "Council Chamber"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2180
msgid "Abandoned Council Chamber"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2221
msgid "The transporter abruptly stops."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2257
msgid "I recognize this corridor. Onwards!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2263
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:123
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:398
msgid "Proceed further underground"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2334
msgid "The Lady of Light and her foolish new cohorts, eh? We should have known that Ergea and her kind couldn’t be trusted. Hopefully you enjoy their company, for we intend to send you all to the abyss together, and not precisely to die..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2340
msgid "The Lady of Light, eh? We should have known that Ergea and her kind couldn’t be trusted. Too bad that your cohorts didn’t make it; we wanted to send you all to the abyss together, and not precisely to die..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. 'Master' here in feminine, referring to Elyssa (the 'Fire').
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2348
msgid "Save your boasting for later — it will not help you win the battle on the surface and we are well accustomed to it at this point. Where is your master?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2353
msgid "Our <i>masters</i> are busy with their own inscrutable plans, and the fortress defenses are already disposing of your pathetic allies above. But it is not <i>your</i> place to ask questions here. Now..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2362
msgid "Would you prefer to go down fighting, or surrender and let us take you to the Fire?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2371
msgid "I’ll let you have a guess."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2386
msgid "... heh. The Fire was right... about you..."
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Demon Spelldancer, id=Talia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2403
msgid "Talia"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Mal Arachgeas
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2484
msgid "Mal Arachgeas"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2581
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3327
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:991
msgid "Is that..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2624
msgid "Those passages appear to lead somewhere."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2720
msgid "A secret passage. Not particularly ingenious. Although... it might lead to the cave Ergea mentioned."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2743
msgid "Wait. There’s someone else in here..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2831
msgid "It’s the other necromancer, member of the Iron Triad. Perhaps, if we take her down... we might be able to force her to give us some directions."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2837
msgid "It’s the other necromancer, member of the Iron Triad. Perhaps, if I take her down... I might be able to force her to give me some directions."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2849
msgid "Defeat Mal Kendria"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2872
msgid "You are the other necromancer from the Iron Triad, aren’t you? Where is your master hiding? Where is the Ruby of Fire?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2886
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3190
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/storytxt.cfg:67
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/storytxt.cfg:73
msgid "(<i>silence</i>)"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2895
msgid "Are you going to answer?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2908
msgid "There is something wrong about her eyes..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2913
msgid "I don’t have time for this."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2940
msgid "Devoid of her own will... and turned into a living puppet... Suddenly, defeating her does not seem to be much of an achievement. I don’t think I saw anything like this the last time I was here. Why would they do this to her, though?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2950
msgid "My lady, we should proceed onwards, quickly. We don’t have much more time, and the Fire of Uria will not take kindly to all these casualties."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2955
msgid "Indeed, let us continue down this passage. If Ergea’s instructions are correct, there is a large stone chamber ahead."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2961
msgid "I should just continue down this passage. If Ergea’s instructions are correct, there is a large stone chamber ahead."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3000
msgid "Move Elynia into the chamber"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3140
msgid "We are trapped in this chamber..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3146
msgid "I am trapped in this chamber..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3170
msgid "(<i>chuckles</i>) That’s were you want us to go. Isn’t that correct... Elyssa?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3176
msgid "(<i>chuckles</i>) That’s were you want me to go. Isn’t that correct... Elyssa?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3199
msgid "You could have opened the gate for me, at the very least."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3209
msgid "Find a way to open the chamber exit gate to proceed"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3264
msgid "Elynia already has the glyph’s spell. Move her next to the chamber exit to open it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3271
msgid "Elynia should be the one to investigate this glyph."
msgstr ""

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3286
msgid "Barrier Spell"
msgstr ""

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3289
msgid "This spell allows the unit to open any barriers that were originally sealed with the same spell."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3302
msgid "Move Elynia next to the chamber exit gate to proceed"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3400
msgid "... So you want me to proceed alone. Very well, then."
msgstr ""

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3630
msgid "You have eight allies on the map already. You cannot recruit additional units at this time!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:227
msgid "I will be truly disappointed if you aren’t waiting behind that gate..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:280
msgid "Elyssa, the Guardian of Darkness"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:280
msgid "Heiress to the Eater of Soul’s Legacy"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:336
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:345
msgid "I have been awaiting this moment for so long, Elyssa. Or should I call you Yechnagoth?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:356
msgid "Yechnagoth is no more."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:390
msgid "Vanquish Elyssa"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:559
msgid "Do you truly believe that such cheap tricks can stop me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:703
msgid "I suppose I may as well call you an impostor then. I have read Argan’s journal — you weren’t destined to possess those powers."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:708
msgid "It was never my choice, dear. And even if it were the case, I have never actually <i>claimed</i> to be Merthiaal."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:717
msgid "I have to admit that you are quite agile for a winged faerie."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:726
msgid "Alas, that will not be sufficient to defeat me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:735
msgid "I had hoped you would have learned new tricks since we last met."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:744
msgid "As much as I would not mind to keep doing this forever..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:749
msgid "You purposefully misled us by removing any references to the final whereabouts of Yechnagoth’s heart from Argan’s journal, didn’t you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:754
msgid "I admit that I took some pages from Argan’s journal some time before you acquired it from him, yes; I also changed a few other things for your <i>convenience</i>."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:759
msgid "You killed Galas before my very eyes. You are responsible for Mal Keshar’s destruction. And for the deaths of millions."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:764
msgid "(<i>chuckles</i>) It was all part of the plan! All those deaths were necessary to appease Uria and prepare our vast stage for this day — the vast stage we normally call ‘Irdya’. My business with that elf you secretly loved was not personal."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:774
msgid "Those who can harness the Aspect of Darkness can read into the minds of weaker creatures at will. Did you not know this?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:783
msgid "Of course you didn’t. You have wasted your entire life pursuing the most banal objectives. You never bothered to try to understand that power you had. Argan and you could have done great things if you had learned what the Union truly entails."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:792
msgid "You have lived awake for over eight hundred years, and yet... you are still an incompetent little brat. Such is the curse of eternal youth, I guess?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:802
msgid "Are you not exhausted already? You sure are persistent. I could end you with a single strike if I wanted..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:807
msgid "THEN WHY DON’T YOU DO IT?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:812
msgid "Is that what you truly want, then? Do you seek the cold touch of death?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:821
msgid "And yet, you fear it. You haven’t been able to bring yourself to put an end to this, but why?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:830
msgid "Is it that you are unable to assume responsibility for your own decisions anymore?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:846
msgid "I see. Frankly, this is quite disappointing. I thought Argan and Galas saw <i>something</i> in you besides your pretty face and hair."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:856
msgid "Oh, my bad. I forgot to mention that... You really want to know, don’t you? Yes, Galas <i>did</i> want to reciprocate your feelings, but he never did so... because you were too busy grieving over Argan’s death like a little girl."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:866
msgid "Perhaps, if you were not so stupid and ignorant of your own power... you would have been able to save Argan in the first place. Don’t you think?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:875
msgid "Shut..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:884
msgid "UP!!!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:992
msgid "... What—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:997
msgid "Heh, heh, heh..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1006
msgid "Good..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1059
msgid "But still not sufficient to defeat a Guardian of Darkness, my dear."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1088
msgid "Most people would call it ‘determination’ — I personally prefer to call it ‘obstinacy’. You truly never give up, do you, Elynia? It is rather tragic, given the circumstances. I suppose that elf sorceress would be proud of you... Hm, what was her name, again?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1135
msgid "That look on your face... You really are some kind of sick and twisted creature, aren’t you? Let’s see how you enjoy <i>this</i> then."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1229
msgid "I had hoped for a fair fight, but in the end it might have merely been wishful thinking on my part. What do you think?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1246
msgid "On the other hand, you are still alive and standing— well, barely, but I am impressed nonetheless."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1251
msgid "What... are you... waiting for..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1256
msgid "Heh."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1262
msgid "My bad — not even you could possibly have the energy to speak while on the verge of death."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1273
msgid "Sweet dreams, my dear."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
