msgid "Only the mightiest demons are allowed to serve Uria as her greatest vassals and governors of the various peoples of Inferno. After the fall of the Chaos Emperor, rumors of the presence of these figures of legend on Irdya abound and instill great fear among the ill-equipped armies of the northern lands."
msgstr ""

