#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Messenger, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Messenger.cfg:23
msgid "Demons without any remarkable fighting skills who survive to adulthood are often employed for more menial tasks. In spite of their condition as slaves of their lords, messengers who can endure all kinds of hazards and serve with unconditional devotion—even if that may require taking their own lives—are a valuable resource in times of war when communication by magic means may fail or be intercepted by the enemy."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Spelldancer, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Spelldancer.cfg:6
