msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Slashing Gale, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Slashing_Gale.cfg:29
msgid "Armed with deadly metal claws and the remarkable flight skills of their stormkind brethren, the Storm Sisters are hired assassins working for the ranks of the Fist of Uria, bearing the mask of his order. Their experience with glamour magic—though limited as it is—allows them to sport wings much like those often acquired by real faerie creatures. In spite of their vain nature, they are dangerously competent as a group — it would take a great degree of foolishness to underestimate their prowess in combat, and even more to expect them to play fair."
msgstr ""

