msgid "On occasion, these aerial demons have been mistaken for faeries and undead spirits of demonkind because of their unusual wings and apparent lack of legs. Formerly unheard of, they can summon strong winds and create great storms for laying waste to forests and villages. When combined with their race’s inherent affinity with fire, the effects can be particularly disastrous."
