#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/angel-of-blood/_initial.cfg:8
msgid "While the history of how the War of Wesmere came to happen is only known to a few elves in the present day, there are even fewer people who know about Zhangor’s true origins. The few records left of his rule in Urvatha speak of his achievements as an implacable warlord who led his people into a slaughter of unprecedented proportions, sealing the fate of shapeshifters for the rest of eternity. Some sources claim that it was this — his most shameful defeat — that led him to take the power of the mythical sentinel between worlds and seek to amplify it using the souls of Irdya’s people as sacrifice."
